Design compatible with:

- Tablet

## Tech

Developed with the Angular Framework

- [Angular](https://angular.io/) - use angular elements for web apps!

## Installation Demo

This demo requires [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) to use npm or you can use the extension of editor VSCode - [Live Server](https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=ritwickdey.LiveServer)

Install the dependencie and start the server.

```sh
npm install --global http-server
http-server index.html
```

And open the console url.
